The,service,provides,measures,of,solar,energy,available,at,specified,locations,on,the,earth,s,surface,Data,give,monthly,mean,values,of,solar,irradiance,measures,for,locations,around,the,globe,Data,reflect,satellite,observations,and,meteorological,observations,and,analyses,from,U,S,government,agencies,the,National,Center,for,Environmental,Predictions,NCEP,and,National,Center,for,Atmospheric,Research,NCAR,Separate,observations,are,rationalized,by,data,fusion,techniques,API,methods,support,submission,of,a,global,location,as,latitude,longitude,and,elevation,The,API,returns,solar,energy,measures,such,as,downwelling,shortwave,irradiance,along,with,low,high,and,average,readings,for,air,temperature,and,relative,humidity